    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Braces or systems of braces, placed between horizontal or vertical structural members, to stiffen them, hold them in place, and to help distribute the load.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
